                "html": "Trolls and <a aonid=\"204\" game-obj=\"Monsters\">ettins</a> do not normally seek one another as mates, but this pairing is the source of the original two-headed trolls\u2014such couplings were engineered and arranged by the cult of <a aonid=\"11\" game-obj=\"Deities\">Lamashtu</a> in ages past. Oblivious to their origin, two-headed trolls tend to give no deference to the Mother of Monsters."
